Seller wants the customer to be able to add valid coupons (Success Case)
“Given that I am a seller using the website
And I want the valid coupons used by the customer to be applied
When the customer opens his cart
And he enters a valid coupon
And he presses on "Apply Coupon"
Then he should see a discount applied on his cart"



Seller wants the customer to be able to add valid coupons (Failure Case)
“Given that I am a seller using the website
And I want the valid coupons used by the customer to be applied
When the customer opens his cart
And he enters a non-valid coupon
And he presses on "Apply Coupon"
Then he should see a message saying "Coupon does not exist"."
